{"tid":1509331,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【學術討論】香城Online前線近戰建議","createTime":"2019-08-26T20:31:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T20:51:33.000Z","uid":291068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e2bc0f7a13421e1db3dcf1768bb7a967b13bc492","tid":1509331,"uid":291068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T20:31:04.000Z","msg":"話說我有個少時打機最鍾意撚狗嘅朋友<br />\n佢睇片見到好多前排玩家拎住碌棍又隊又扑<br />\n佢話敵方拎盾 應該主力攻佢下盤 拎棍橫掃對腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過明白大家都係乖學生<br />\n當刻醒唔起係好正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢仲同我講 打PVP習慣咗行近敵方再突然踎低<br />\n然後雙臂攬實佢雙腿再用力一抽<br />\n只要夠力實撻到攤攤腰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過呢個極近距離有相當大風險被扣血<br />\n而且敵方後腦著地可能即時quit game<br />\n非逼不得已都唔好諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有佢話洗潔精唔係最佳選項<br />\n可以用皮革舖嘅膠水 乾咗啲怪衝埋嚟就癡到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53262d367d27d88dc64e8c5ca16233049e00e08b","tid":1509331,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T20:31:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hjf7rg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hjf7rg.gif&h=994c84f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrmsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=bf67522d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrmsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=d6670781\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=